---
// The single strongest authenticity asset — featured as its own block
---

<section class="honesty-callout section--slate">
  <div class="container honesty-inner">
    <div class="honesty-content reveal">
      <div class="honesty-eyebrow">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 0 0 1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 0 0 1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 0 0 .806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 0 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 0 1-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 0 0-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 0-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 0 0 .806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 0 1 3.138-3.138z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Why customers trust us</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="honesty-headline">
        "We told them not to buy the expensive part."
      </h2>

      <blockquote class="honesty-quote">
        <p>
          "DMV Appliance was great. They inspected our washer for free. Showed us what was wrong.
          The service tech said, <em>'I can't let you buy that, it's too expensive'</em> — so he fixed
          the part instead of replacing it."
        </p>
        <footer>
          <cite>— Thumbtack review</cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>

      <p class="honesty-context">
        Pir has been repairing appliances in the DMV since 2007. He's seen every model, every failure mode.
        When a repair doesn't make financial sense, he tells you. No upselling. No manufactured urgency.
        Just an honest answer so you can make the right call for your home.
      </p>

      <div class="honesty-actions">
        <a href="#booking" class="btn btn--primary">Request a Callback</a>
        <a href="/about/" class="honesty-about-link">
          Learn about our approach
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="honesty-stat-col reveal" style="transition-delay: 120ms">
      <div class="honesty-stats">
        <div class="honesty-stat">
          <span class="honesty-stat-num">18+</span>
          <span class="honesty-stat-label">Years serving the DMV</span>
        </div>
        <div class="honesty-stat">
          <span class="honesty-stat-num">4.8★</span>
          <span class="honesty-stat-label">50+ reviews on Thumbtack</span>
        </div>
        <div class="honesty-stat">
          <span class="honesty-stat-num">$60</span>
          <span class="honesty-stat-label">off every completed repair</span>
        </div>
        <div class="honesty-stat">
          <span class="honesty-stat-num">1 visit</span>
          <span class="honesty-stat-label">Most repairs, no second trip</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .honesty-callout {
    background-color: var(--color-slate);
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
  }

  .honesty-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .honesty-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  /* Eyebrow */
  .honesty-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--font-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  /* Headline */
  .honesty-headline {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 0.5rem, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Quote */
  .honesty-quote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .honesty-quote p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .honesty-quote em {
    color: #fff;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .honesty-quote footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  .honesty-quote cite {
    font-size: var(--font-small);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* Context paragraph */
  .honesty-context {
    font-size: var(--font-body);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  /* Actions */
  .honesty-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .honesty-about-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-1);
    font-size: var(--font-small);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      color var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out),
      gap var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out);
  }

  @media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
    .honesty-about-link:hover {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }
  }

  /* Stat column */
  .honesty-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .honesty-stat {
    background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .honesty-stat-num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .honesty-stat-label {
    font-size: var(--font-xs);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: none;
  }
</style>
